<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:07:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列安全内阁将男性义务兵役期延长至三年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-security-cabinet-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-a682-da1a-adf0-a69f072f0000</link><description>将男性服役期限延长 4 个月的立法将于周日提交议会。这一决定是在加沙战争和黎巴嫩边境局势升级期间军队面临兵员短缺的情况下做出的</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 12:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-security-cabinet-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-a682-da1a-adf0-a69f072f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认以色列和埃及就埃及-加沙边境以色列国防军的替代方案进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/cease-fire-negotiations-explore-tech-alternatives-to-israeli-troops-on-gaza-egypt-border/00000190-a619-da1a-adf0-a69dd10c0000</link><description>据报道，停火协议谈判代表正在讨论加沙和埃及边境沿线的电子监视系统，该系统可以让以色列从该地区撤军。总理办公室称其为“假新闻”</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/cease-fire-negotiations-explore-tech-alternatives-to-israeli-troops-on-gaza-egypt-border/00000190-a619-da1a-adf0-a69dd10c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军计算机负责人表示，战争期间陆军云系统成为数十亿次网络攻击的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-computer-chief-says-army-cloud-system-targeted-by-billions-of-cyberattacks-during-war/00000190-a601-da1a-adf0-a69d08d00000</link><description>这些攻击针对以色列军队的主要作战云计算系统，其中包括地面部队用于管理战斗、定位部队和共享实时信息的软件</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-computer-chief-says-army-cloud-system-targeted-by-billions-of-cyberattacks-during-war/00000190-a601-da1a-adf0-a69d08d00000</guid></item><item><title>绝望面前，一线希望：人质家属游行前往耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-face-of-despair-a-glimmer-of-hope-hostages-families-march-to-jerusalem/00000190-a5c6-d510-a5dc-efced8170000</link><description>周三，数百名抗议者前往总理办公室，试图迫使内塔尼亚胡批准该协议。 “比比知道我们的目光在他身上，我们告诉他不要破坏这笔交易，”人质的母亲说道</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:43:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-face-of-despair-a-glimmer-of-hope-hostages-families-march-to-jerusalem/00000190-a5c6-d510-a5dc-efced8170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周四在以色列北部无人机袭击中丧生的以色列预备役军人姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reservist-killed-in-thursdays-drone-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-a55e-dbad-adfc-f5df130b0000</link><description>军士长。 （res.）瓦列里·切福诺夫（Valeri Chefonov）在真主党袭击以色列北部后受重伤，后来因伤势过重而死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reservist-killed-in-thursdays-drone-attack-in-northern-israel/00000190-a55e-dbad-adfc-f5df130b0000</guid></item><item><title>对哈马斯协议的乐观情绪从华盛顿蔓延到以色列高层。内塔尼亚胡还有其他担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/optimism-over-hamas-deal-reaches-israels-top-brass-netanyahu-has-other-concerns/00000190-a39e-da1a-adf0-a79f61580000</link><description>更可能的情况是，依赖极右翼伙伴的内塔尼亚胡将推迟回应，直到国会演讲之后。在那之后，就不难找到退出谈判的借口了</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/optimism-over-hamas-deal-reaches-israels-top-brass-netanyahu-has-other-concerns/00000190-a39e-da1a-adf0-a79f61580000</guid></item><item><title>当紧要关头，内塔尼亚胡将取消人质协议以拯救他的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/when-push-comes-to-shove-netanyahu-will-nix-a-hostage-deal-to-save-his-coalition/00000190-a2f1-ddf1-abb6-eff1431e0000</link><description>关于加沙停火和释放人质协议的谈判所取得的进展纯粹是理论上的，因为以色列政府中的极右部长拥有否决权 ■ 与哈马斯的协议之争可能是国防部长约夫·加兰特的政治绝唱</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:08:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/when-push-comes-to-shove-netanyahu-will-nix-a-hostage-deal-to-save-his-coalition/00000190-a2f1-ddf1-abb6-eff1431e0000</guid></item><item><title>“在战争期间，面对以色列军队服役，我们意识到生活并不永远”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-12/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-middle-of-war-facing-israeli-army-service-we-realized-that-life-is-not-forever/00000190-a4a4-dd20-abfa-feb7a24f0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：以色列高中生思考 10 月 7 日后世界的未来，一对夫妇在结婚 15 年后首次出国度假</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 02:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-12/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-middle-of-war-facing-israeli-army-service-we-realized-that-life-is-not-forever/00000190-a4a4-dd20-abfa-feb7a24f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列建国前的第一次政治暗杀的影响在 100 年后才显现出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/the-repercussions-of-israels-first-political-assassination-are-felt-100-years-later/00000190-a1b2-dd20-abfa-ffb7b3b70000</link><description>在建国前的伊舒夫，一位颓废的同性恋诗人拒绝随着犹太复国主义-社会主义的曲调起舞，比魔鬼还要糟糕。刺杀雅各布·德哈恩的目的是为了震慑任何敢于越界的人。这种恐怖在今天的以色列仍然普遍存在</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/the-repercussions-of-israels-first-political-assassination-are-felt-100-years-later/00000190-a1b2-dd20-abfa-ffb7b3b70000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦报道：四名国际援助人员在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-live/biden-gaps-remain-between-israel-and-hamas-but-were-making-progress/00000190-a48d-da1a-adf0-a69d984e0000</link><description>以色列国防军预备役军人在以色列北部真主党无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 导弹落入以色列北部，导致停电 ■ 以色列和埃及在停火谈判中讨论加沙和埃及边境的反走私监视系统 ■ 拜登：以色列和哈马斯之间仍存在分歧，但我们正在取得进展 ■ 地区议会称，两枚导弹落在北部城镇梅图拉，导致停电</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-live/biden-gaps-remain-between-israel-and-hamas-but-were-making-progress/00000190-a48d-da1a-adf0-a69d984e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端正统派网络将国家资金从女童教育转移到让孩子们信仰宗教的学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/haredi-network-diverts-state-funds-from-girls-education-toward-turning-kids-religious/00000190-a2ee-d852-abfb-e3fe00990000</link><description>联合托拉犹太教学校系统从女童的教育中抽走了数亿谢克尔，并将其转移到旨在让儿童更接近宗教的学校。一位《国土报》记者穿上基帕帽参观了这些机构，发现了一个旨在让以色列变得更加正统的精品框架——由世俗纳税人买单</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/haredi-network-diverts-state-funds-from-girls-education-toward-turning-kids-religious/00000190-a2ee-d852-abfb-e3fe00990000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：回想起来，我希望我能够说服以色列人在加沙战争期间做很多事情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-i-wish-i-had-been-able-to-convince-israel-to-do-more-do-during-gaza-war/00000190-a45a-ddf1-abb6-eddbeae90000</link><description>美国总统在北约峰会新闻发布会上表示，以色列在击败哈马斯后无法重新占领加沙，并称内塔尼亚胡内阁是该国历史上“最保守”的内阁</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-i-wish-i-had-been-able-to-convince-israel-to-do-more-do-during-gaza-war/00000190-a45a-ddf1-abb6-eddbeae90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列独立媒体的愈演愈烈的攻击暴露了他的脆弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-intensifying-attack-on-israels-independent-media-reveals-his-fragility/00000190-a271-da1a-adf0-a6fdb0cf0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡重塑媒体的努力是政治生存的战略举措，包括任命效忠者并确保专家认同他的观点。 10 月 7 日之后和加沙战争期间，这场运动愈演愈烈</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 20:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-intensifying-attack-on-israels-independent-media-reveals-his-fragility/00000190-a271-da1a-adf0-a6fdb0cf0000</guid></item><item><title>允许以色列古物管理局在西岸运作相当于吞并</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/allowing-israel-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank-is-equivalent-to-annexation/00000190-a32c-ddf1-abb6-efedbd390000</link><description>利库德集团议员阿米特·哈勒维提交的一项法案的通过将在这些领土上适用以色列法律，实际上为那些声称以色列在西岸实行种族隔离政权的人服务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 20:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/allowing-israel-antiquities-authority-to-operate-in-west-bank-is-equivalent-to-annexation/00000190-a32c-ddf1-abb6-efedbd390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回 10 月 7 日被捕的六名加沙人的上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denied-appeals-of-six-gazans-arrested-on-october-7/00000190-a32d-d962-a3b7-b3bfae910000</link><description>这六人涉嫌参与大屠杀，但声称他们进入以色列是为了找工作，法院表示他们正在进行的调查是一项“复杂”的调查。司法部长莱文：“我的部门不会资助哈马斯恐怖分子的防御”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 19:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denied-appeals-of-six-gazans-arrested-on-october-7/00000190-a32d-d962-a3b7-b3bfae910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方拦截价值 2750 万美元的可卡因进入该国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/israeli-police-stops-27-5-million-worth-of-cocaine-entering-the-country/00000190-a31e-dbad-adfc-f79f0f7a0000</link><description>三人因涉嫌“以色列近代历史上最大的可卡因交易之一”而被警方逮捕，其中一人是 10 月 7 日诺瓦狂欢大屠杀的幸存者</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 19:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/israeli-police-stops-27-5-million-worth-of-cocaine-entering-the-country/00000190-a31e-dbad-adfc-f79f0f7a0000</guid></item><item><title>首位加沙战争以色列依良心拒服兵役者在入狱六个月后获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/first-conscientious-objector-of-the-gaza-war-freed-after-more-than-six-months-in-prison/00000190-a301-da1a-adf0-a79de1290000</link><description>过去十年，18 岁的塔尔·米特尼克 (Tal Mitnick) 在监狱里度过的时间比任何其他以色列依良心拒服兵役者都要多。军队尚未提供他豁免服役的理由，他的律师表示，此举在此类案件中是史无前例的</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 19:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/first-conscientious-objector-of-the-gaza-war-freed-after-more-than-six-months-in-prison/00000190-a301-da1a-adf0-a79de1290000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里 10 月 7 日调查揭示的以色列军队的失败只是问题的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-failure-revealed-in-beeri-oct-7-probe-is-only-part-of-the-picture/00000190-a2e9-d962-a3b7-b2ff646f0000</link><description>调查结果的很大一部分是优先顺序有缺陷、指挥官犯下的错误以及军队采取行动所花费的大量时间。但这不应转移人们对政治层面失败的注意力</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-failure-revealed-in-beeri-oct-7-probe-is-only-part-of-the-picture/00000190-a2e9-d962-a3b7-b2ff646f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 279 天：以色列国防部长呼吁调查哈马斯获得权力的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-279-defense-minister-calls-to-probe-conditions-that-empowered-hamas/00000190-a2bc-ddf1-abb6-effd7f930001</link><description>以色列人在以色列北部真主党无人机袭击中身受重伤 ■ 辛贝特酋长率领的以色列代表团前往开罗继续停战谈判 ■ 以色列国防军公布 10 月 7 日贝埃里基布兹事件的调查结果 ■ 以色列国防部长呼吁建立国家调查委员会“在过去十年中导致哈马斯权力建立的条件” ■ 战争开始 279 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 17:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-279-defense-minister-calls-to-probe-conditions-that-empowered-hamas/00000190-a2bc-ddf1-abb6-effd7f930001</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府采取重大举措，寻求对土耳其进口商品实施贸易禁运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/in-a-drastic-step-israeli-government-seeks-trade-embargo-on-imports-from-turkey/00000190-a1b0-dbad-adfc-f5b907e50000</link><description>总理办公室发布了一项史无前例的提案，全面禁止从土耳其直接进口以色列。以色列商会联合会主席认为此举是以色列战争的另一条战线的开辟，这是以色列消费者无法承受的</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 17:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/in-a-drastic-step-israeli-government-seeks-trade-embargo-on-imports-from-turkey/00000190-a1b0-dbad-adfc-f5b907e50000</guid></item></channel></rss>